# University Course Management System

A comprehensive console-based Java application for managing university operations, including users, courses, enrollments, grades, and reports. This project demonstrates core Object-Oriented Programming (OOP) principles: **Inheritance, Polymorphism, Encapsulation, and Abstraction**.

